Этот план необходимо скачать до начала м: This plan needs to be downloaded before the start of the marathon and followed throughout the project!
plan_note_1: As these are the first two weeks and it's essential to acclimate to the workload, the number of sets will mainly be two to three. Aim for 15-20 repetitions per set.
plan_note_2: The first two weeks are focused on building endurance, so expect a high number of repetitions. If you have experience and have been active for a while, from the second week onwards, you can follow this plan with 10-12 repetitions and 3-4 sets.
plan_note_3: But be cautious – choose a weight that's right for you. Pay attention to what needs to be done in a superset (indicated by matching letters) and what should be done separately.
additional-day-comment2: Rest or get active – your choice. I recommend combining cardio with core exercises. 40-60 minutes on any cardio machine + 150/200 crunches.
